                                            {
                                                "text": "<i>What color is it? &#x02192; It is purple / orange / green / pink</i>"
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "text": "<i>What is it? &#x02192; It is a/an Ecco / grape / flower / glove / hopping horse / carrot/ yarn / cat / button / dinosaur / tree / mitten / wig / shoes / horn / pig</i>"
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "text": "Asks students to repeat vocabulary. Teacher corrects their pronunciation"
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "text": "Teacher instructs students to say whole sentences and corrects their pronunciation",
